The PlaiiinLight client app talks to PlaiiinLightOS firmware (in the
`lampos/` directory of this repository) over a documented HTTP, WebSocket,
and BLE protocol. The firmware itself is licensed separately under the
Apache License, Version 2.0 — see `lampos/LICENSE`. The protocol contract
is published at `lampos/docs/protocol.md`; third parties are free to implement
their own clients against it.
